      <title>鸽派美联储推动金价首次突破每盎司 2,200 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者对美联储降息路径信心增强，金价首次飙升至每盎司2200美元以上，从而增强了无息黄金的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/spot-gold-rises-to-2-200-an-ounce-for-the-first-time</guid>
